---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import davidAshford from '../assets/david-ashford.png';
---

<section class="pad-sm" id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div class="portrait reveal">
      <Image
        src={davidAshford}
        alt="David Ashford, founder of Aurel Creative"
        width={600}
        height={600}
        class="portrait-img"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="about reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 120ms">
      <p class="eyebrow">Who you work with</p>
      <h2>Founder-led, kept lean on purpose.</h2>
      <p>
        David Ashford spent five years building brand identities and content systems for a London
        agency before starting Aurel Creative around one idea. The creators who attach the right
        product to their audience build real income with almost no overhead.
      </p>
      <p>
        He built Aurel to be the team that handles that product end to end, so creators keep doing
        what they are good at. Behind him is a small group of writers, designers, and subject
        specialists who keep the work senior and the operation quiet.
      </p>
      <p class="sig">David Ashford<small>Founder, Aurel Creative</small></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .portrait {
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(150deg, #e9ecf5, #dde2ee);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .portrait-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .about p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 54ch;
  }

  .about p.eyebrow {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .sig {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .sig small {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .portrait {
      max-width: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
